<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.These Regulations with all 16 articles were promulgated per Order of Ministry of Interior No. Tai-Nei-Yi-Zi-0980959975 dated June 1, 2009 in conjunction with Order of the Ministry of Justice No. Fa-Jian-Zi-0980021933 also dated June 1, 2009.
